Package: easycsv
Type: Package
Title: Load Multiple 'csv' and 'txt' Tables
Date: 2017-08-01
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Dror", "Bogin", email = "dror.bogin@gmail.com",role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains functions for easily loading multiple comma separated tables into R's global environment.
    easycsv allows users to read multiple comma separated tables from a local directory, a zip file or a zip file on a remote directory. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: GPL-2
URL: https://github.com/bogind/easycsv
BugReports: https://github.com/bogind/easycsv/issues
